      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw, F1717 fixture) is the same geometry and loading mode as the COU; no extrapolation required.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses the identical screw design (non-cannulated 7.5 mm, same production lot) in the identical ASTM F1717 compression-bending fixture. No geometric or loading extrapolation is required between validation scenario and COU. Validation activities are fully relevant."
    }
